metadata.name: The Emperor
metadata.description:
The Emperor Tarot card means willpower, logical actions, achievement of the goal, correctness of the chosen path. It can symbolize success, fatherhood, and in some cases stabilization of the situation, legal income.

Ethereal Journey Tarot is a collaborative deck where each card is individually designed by a different international artist.

2224 x 3840 pxl

May 19, 2023
J_SKY
